data.description: Location! Location! Location! Don't miss this opportunity to invest in this highly desirable Roselle Neighborhood! Boasting an impressive half acre of land on a corner lot. This home features plenty of space to spread out, including 4 bedrooms, a dine in kitchen, dining room/living room combo and a spacious cozy downstairs, with a fireplace. Beautiful hardwood flooring throughout! Attached 2 car garage with storage. Outside the home has plenty of space to enjoy! Deck off the kitchen, and back patio with plenty of yard for entertaining. Did I Mention it is in a very highly rated school district just steps to parks? Furnace and A/C  Dec 2021, and water heater new as of 2020. Home is selling As-Is.
